# Patch file for enhanced-automation.service.ts
# This describes the changes needed

## Problem:
Keys are captured from getLastOpRevision BEFORE clicking into a chat.
The system returns immediately when keys are captured, without waiting for getRecentMessagesV2.

## Solution:
1. Don't return immediately when keys are captured
2. Continue clicking into chat to trigger getRecentMessagesV2
3. Only return after getRecentMessagesV2 cURL is captured (or timeout)

## Key changes:
1. Remove early return when keys are captured
2. Continue attempts even after keys are captured (to get getRecentMessagesV2)
3. Only return when BOTH keys AND getRecentMessagesV2 cURL are captured
